text: "Nada Nuevo" (English: "Nothing New") is a song by Mexican singer-songwriter Christian Nodal released on February 14, 2019 as a single. "Nada Nuevo" was witten by Nodal and American songwriter and producer Edgar Barrera. "Nada Nuevo" reached number one on the Top 20 General Mexican Songs Chart and number twenty six on the Billboard Top Latin Songs chart in the United States. ==Charts== {| class="wikitable sortable" !Chart (2019) !Peak position |- | Mexico Top 20 General (Monitor Latino) |align="center"|1 |- |- |- |} ===Year-end charts=== {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center" |- ! scope="col"| Chart (2019) ! scope="col"| Position |- ! scope="row"| Mexico Top 20 General (Monitor Latino) |align="center"|15 |- ! scope="row"| US Hot Latin Songs (Billboard)https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2019/hot-latin-songs | 75 |} ==Certifications== ==See also== *List of number-one songs of 2019 (Mexico) ==References== Category:2019 songs Category:2019 singles Category:Mexican folk songs Category:Ranchera songs Category:Spanish-language songs Category:Universal Music Latin Entertainment singles Category:Monitor Latino Top General number-one singles Category:Christian Nodal songs Category:Songs written by Edgar Barrera Category:Songs written by Christian Nodal Category:Billboard Regional Mexican Songs number-one singles
